            function generateUUID() {\n
              var d = new Date().getTime();\n
              var uuid = 'xxxxxxxx-xxxx-4xxx-yxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx'.replace(/[xy]/g, function(\n
                c\n
              ) {\n
                var r = ((d + Math.random() * 16) % 16) | 0;\n
                d = Math.floor(d / 16);\n
                return (c == 'x' ? r : (r & 0x7) | 0x8).toString(16);\n
              });\n
              return uuid;\n
            }\n

            var lzdDocCookies = {\n
              getItem: function(sKey) {\n
                return (\n
                  decodeURIComponent(\n
                    document.cookie.replace(\n
                      new RegExp(\n
                        '(?:(?:^|.*;)\\s*' +\n
                          encodeURIComponent(sKey).replace(/[\-\.\+\*]/g, '\\$&') +\n
                          '\\s*\\=\\s*([^;]*).*$)|^.*$'\n
                      ),\n
                      '$1'\n
                    )\n
                  ) || null\n
                );\n
              },\n
              setItem: function(sKey, sValue, vEnd, sPath, sDomain, bSecure) {\n
                if (!sKey || /^(?:expires|max\-age|path|domain|secure)$/i.test(sKey)) {\n
                  return false;\n
                }\n
                var sExpires = '';\n
                var exdate = new Date();\n
                exdate.setDate(exdate.getDate() + vEnd);\n
                sExpires = ';expires=' + exdate.toGMTString();\n
                document.cookie =\n
                  encodeURIComponent(sKey) +\n
                  '=' +\n
                  encodeURIComponent(sValue) +\n
                  sExpires +\n
                  (sDomain ? '; domain=' + sDomain : '') +\n
                  (sPath ? '; path=' + sPath : '; path=/') +\n
                  (bSecure ? '; secure' : '');\n
                return true;\n
              },\n
              hasItem: function(sKey) {\n
                if (!sKey) {\n
                  return false;\n
                }\n
                return new RegExp(\n
                  '(?:^|;\\s*)' +\n
                    encodeURIComponent(sKey).replace(/[\-\.\+\*]/g, '\\$&') +\n
                    '\\s*\\='\n
                ).test(document.cookie);\n
              },\n
              removeItem: function(sKey, sPath, sDomain) {\n
                if (!this.hasItem(sKey)) {\n
                  return false;\n
                }\n
                document.cookie =\n
                  encodeURIComponent(sKey) +\n
                  '=; expires=Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:00 GMT' +\n
                  (sDomain ? '; domain=' + sDomain : '') +\n
                  (sPath ? '; path=' + sPath : '; path=/');\n

            var UUID = generateUUID();\n
            var t_uid = lzdDocCookies.getItem('t_uid');\n
            var anon_uid = lzdDocCookies.getItem('anon_uid');\n
            for (var i = 0; i < LZD_HOST_ARRAY.length; i++) {\n
              if (window.location.host.indexOf(LZD_HOST_ARRAY[i]) > -1) {\n

                window.LZD = window.LZD || {};\n
                window.LZD.updateBreadcrumb = function (list) {\n
                    if (!list || !list instanceof Array) {\n
                        return;\n
                    }\n
                    var parentNode = document.getElementById('J_breadcrumb');\n
                    while(parentNode.hasChildNodes()) {  \n
                        parentNode.removeChild(parentNode.firstChild);  \n

                    var size = list.length;\n
                    for (var i = 0; i < size; i++) {\n
                        var item = list[i];\n
                        var liNode = document.createElement("li");\n
                        liNode.className = 'breadcrumb_item';\n
                        if (i === size - 1) {\n

                                '</a>' +\n
                                '<div class="breadcrumb_right_arrow"></div>' +\n
                            '</span>';\n
                        }\n
                        parentNode.appendChild(liNode);\n

                    var breadcrumbListNode = document.getElementById('J_breadcrumb_list');\n
